00:03:54.860 --> 00:04:03.100
Yesterday, we have had a nice meditation,
and we all felt the cool breeze of the Holy

00:04:03.109 --> 00:04:18.540
Ghost, and I told you that we have to understand
that this is the greatest moment in the history,

00:04:18.540 --> 00:04:30.380
while you are born, and you are doing the
highest work, that is of God, here. And you

00:04:30.380 --> 00:04:40.000
are specially chosen for it and how you must
know that you are a saint.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:46.500
Apart from this, all the blessings that you
have, you also get lost sometimes in your

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:56.070
blessings and start behaving in a manner which
doesn’t behove a saintly person. Now after

00:04:56.070 --> 00:05:10.840
so many years I have agreed or I agreed to
have Ekadesha Rudra Puja, which was, I know

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:15.110
was a dangerous thing to do because I know
still so many Sahaja Yogis are half-baked,

00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:20.970
some are just taking advantage of Sahaja Yoga,
and making money out of it or getting some

00:05:20.970 --> 00:05:28.100
power out of it, or fame, or something.
So this was let loose now, this power, and

00:05:28.100 --> 00:05:34.270
is a very, very dangerous power in a way,
and you have to be very careful. It of course

00:05:34.270 --> 00:05:40.210
protects you from the people who attack you
and try to destroy you from all negativity.

00:05:40.210 --> 00:05:47.380
It wants to work out all kinds of protection
that is possible for you, but if you start

00:05:47.380 --> 00:05:53.450
misbehaving, also it can act upon you.
I’ll give you a story about something happened

00:05:53.450 --> 00:06:04.370
very recently in India. One Sahaja Yogi went
to another Sahaja Yogi’s place, who had

00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:10.870
lots of jackfruits in her garden. And she
said, “Why don’t you give me one jackfruit

00:06:10.870 --> 00:06:15.020
because I want to make some vegetable out
of it.” So she said, “Not today. I’ll

00:06:15.020 --> 00:06:21.550
give you some other day; I don’t want to
give you today.” That’s all. And she had

00:06:21.550 --> 00:06:27.470
lots of jackfruits. So the Sahaja Yogi felt
bad, that you see, she just wanted to make

00:06:27.470 --> 00:06:33.330
some vegetables for some nice people coming
to her house. Costs you nothing in the market,

00:06:33.330 --> 00:06:39.900
just she liked the jackfruit so she said “Can
I have one jackfruit?” Next day there was

00:06:39.900 --> 00:06:49.630
a very big wind, a kind of a typhoon came,
only in her garden, nowhere else. And all

00:06:49.630 --> 00:06:57.220
her jackfruits fell down. Also, the tree fell
down. And she didn’t know what to do so

00:06:57.220 --> 00:07:03.120
she came back and she said to this, another
Sahaja Yogini, “I’m sorry I’ve said

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:10.800
these things. That is what has happened. Now
you please save me from another disaster because

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:18.840
I have been rather selfish towards myself.”
She said, “No, I never said anything to

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:22.990
Mother. I never told Her. I just came back
home, I forgot everything. I never told anything

00:07:22.990 --> 00:07:31.770
to Mother. I never carried any malice in my
mind. I was absolutely very forgiving. How

00:07:31.770 --> 00:07:39.110
it has happened?” This has happened after
the Ekadesha Rudra Puja and she was worried

00:07:39.110 --> 00:07:44.960
that all her garden will be swept away one
day. So she wrote a letter to Me saying, Mother,

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:50.930
this is what has happened. I have done it
because I have these bad habits from my past

00:07:50.930 --> 00:08:00.740
life, and I tried to save one jackfruit and
then she had to give it away to beggars, to

00:08:00.740 --> 00:08:08.320
servants. Nobody would buy those jackfruits
from her. Then she lost all her money. She

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:14.830
lost everything.
I know it is rather dangerous but how to destroy

00:08:14.830 --> 00:08:21.830
the negativity? And today I find the negativity
is also hurting Sahaja Yoga, very much, and

00:08:21.830 --> 00:08:27.240
Sahaja Yogis. Through a very subtle method.
As you must have heard about Australia, what

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:35.449
has happened there. One lady who was sent
from her husband to Australia to get corrected.

00:08:35.449 --> 00:08:41.469
So there’s another one who’s a wife of
someone. She’s very conscious of her “wifeness.”

00:08:41.469 --> 00:08:50.720
She got hold of this negative woman and created
a group of negative such women. And all the

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:56.829
vibrations of Sahaja Yoga were finished there.
On My birthday, not one person sent Me even

00:08:56.829 --> 00:09:05.819
a flower from Australia. They did my puja,
all right. That ritual they did, puja. But

00:09:05.819 --> 00:09:12.709
families. She said that we are doing in our
own family. Which is your family? This small

00:09:12.709 --> 00:09:20.740
little family of ashram, or your own family?
And the whole thing got destroyed. All the

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:28.949
vibrations of all the Australians was destroyed.
Then I had to call the leader to Bombay. He

00:09:28.949 --> 00:09:33.759
was so upset with his own vibrations because
started shaking before me. His hands started

00:09:33.759 --> 00:09:41.079
trembling before me. He said, “I am sensitive.”
I said, “No, this is bhoot, this is not

00:09:41.079 --> 00:09:44.829
sensitivity. If you get anything, pains, or
anything like that, that means you’re a

00:09:44.829 --> 00:09:49.410
bhoot. You’re not sensitive. Don’t be
diverted. Don’t think like that. Don’t

00:09:49.410 --> 00:09:55.009
have wrong ideas about yourself.” I said,
“You sit down before me now.” Then I took

00:09:55.009 --> 00:10:01.930
out the spirits from him. Then he admitted
there was an “Assault of Scottish people

00:10:01.930 --> 00:10:06.980
on me, Scottish people”. Why? Because she
went from Scotland. I said, “Bhoots do not

00:10:06.980 --> 00:10:12.329
have any nationality. They do not have any
cast. They don’t have any religion. They

00:10:12.329 --> 00:10:18.180
are bhoots. So don’t call them Scottish.
They could be Russians. They could be Italians.

00:10:18.180 --> 00:10:23.899
They could be Indians. They could be anything.”
But such a lot them that the whole of Australia,

00:10:23.899 --> 00:10:30.660
the whole of New York got caught up.
So how the negativity crawls into it and a

00:10:30.660 --> 00:10:37.899
person like James who is a saint was hurt.
Not hurt but he was absolutely ruined and

00:10:37.899 --> 00:10:43.110
he admitted that Mother, I know what has happened.
But I found out his wife who was guilty. She

00:10:43.110 --> 00:10:48.649
had a very bad past. Allergic to things. [SHE
WAS…del] All kinds of things she had. I

00:10:48.649 --> 00:10:56.689
told her that you have to get out of Australia.
So the Maha puja has been postponed in a way.

00:10:56.689 --> 00:11:01.370
I’ll see to it that we do it but may not
be any one of the Sahaja Yogis from that ashram

00:11:01.370 --> 00:11:09.110
come. And then to my surprise, all these horrible
six women who had formed a group with this

00:11:09.110 --> 00:11:15.850
woman, wrote a letter to me that “She has
uplifted us.” And the vibrations were so

00:11:15.850 --> 00:11:21.089
bad that I just felt the whole vibrations
started flowing and fighting with them. I

00:11:21.089 --> 00:11:26.800
couldn’t read the letter. And they felt
they have been uplifted. So in Sahaja Yoga,

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:34.730
you can be misled very much by so many things.
But now, be careful. Don’t try to cheat

00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:40.790
yourself. Must understand your own value.
As I told you yesterday that you are yogis,

00:11:40.790 --> 00:11:46.579
you are saints, and you should not yield to
anything nonsensical and cheapish. Anybody

00:11:46.579 --> 00:11:49.839
who tries to do all those things, you should
tell them “You are yogis.”

00:11:49.839 --> 00:11:57.329
As I told you yesterday that for a person
who is a yogi, [HINDI phrase] the whole world

00:11:57.329 --> 00:12:04.709
is his own family. Specially it is very much
in Europe, I find, and England and America.

00:12:04.709 --> 00:12:10.509
The women have become very dominant. And they
know how to control men by telling them stories

00:12:10.509 --> 00:12:17.850
about how to look after the family, how to
look after the children, how to do that. Sometimes

00:12:17.850 --> 00:12:27.790
it’s amazing. And you get lost with it.
I have seen so many of like that. It has created

00:12:27.790 --> 00:12:33.399
so many problems. Now I request all the women
to behave themselves and understand they are

00:12:33.399 --> 00:12:37.600
wives. And whatever blessings they have got
from Sahaja Yoga will be all withdrawn if

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:43.249
you start misbehaving. And all kinds of miseries
will be upon them, not because of Me but because

00:12:43.249 --> 00:12:50.199
of Ekadesha Rudra. As you put everything on
the bhoots, let Me put it on all the deities.

00:12:50.199 --> 00:12:54.399
I don’t take any responsibility. Because
if you are irresponsible, they’ll hit you

00:12:54.399 --> 00:13:00.540
hard and you will end up with cancer or something
very serious and then, don’t blame me. This

00:13:00.540 --> 00:13:07.069
is the situation today. I have known some
Sahaja Yoginis who confessed to me that they

00:13:07.069 --> 00:13:13.319
have been doing this, they have been doing
that. They have been talking about families–this,

00:13:13.319 --> 00:13:20.220
that. And they have been hurt. This is to
be understood because I think the women in

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:26.059
the West do not have intelligence. They are
not intelligent. That’s the simple equation

00:13:26.059 --> 00:13:30.470
I have reached. Some have intelligence and
