in the North India, I should say, that women

00:15:46.899 --> 00:15:51.610
are very much dominated. We had one Sahaja
Yogini. Her husband was a Sahaja Yogi, he

00:15:51.610 --> 00:15:57.589
was a doctor. He got paralysis. When he got
paralysis, his wife started earning money.

00:15:57.589 --> 00:16:05.550
