humiliated. Then he dominated her much more.

00:16:05.550 --> 00:16:09.410
She came and told me, “It was nice when
I was not earning — he was much sweeter

00:16:09.410 --> 00:16:16.129
to me…now I’m earning…” And she was
giving every single pie to him. Still he was

00:16:16.129 --> 00:16:20.529
dominating her all the time. “Why you didn’t
do this? Why you didn’t do that?” She

00:16:20.529 --> 00:16:25.329
said, “Never did that before. As soon as
he’s all right, I’m going to give up my

00:16:25.329 --> 00:16:31.429
earnings,” she said, “because my husband
cannot stand my earnings.”

00:16:31.429 --> 00:16:36.220
So I have to request you people, first and
foremost thing, all the Sahaja Yoginis must

00:16:36.220 --> 00:16:43.189
know Sahaja Yoga as well as the men know.
