00:17:20.630 --> 00:17:26.240
Yoga. Only they want to use Sahaja Yoga sometimes
to dominate the husbands. One has to face

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:36.090
it up. How much do you know deeply about Sahaja
Yoga? Most of you have so many problems within

00:17:36.090 --> 00:17:40.740
yourselves. As I have seen, some of you, as
