perfect, in perfect health and perfect knowledge

00:18:06.799 --> 00:18:12.730
about Sahaja Yoga you should have. How many
of you have read Advent? Let us see. How many

00:18:12.730 --> 00:18:30.039
of you have read full Advent? Alright. That’s
