00:19:05.260 --> 00:19:14.190
about in knowledge about Sahaja Yoga? How
many have given realizations to others? Raise

00:19:14.190 --> 00:19:25.010
your hands. Only the women I am interested
in. That’s good. So that is what one should

00:19:25.010 --> 00:19:35.559
be proud of. One should know how much you
know Sahaja Yoga mentally, emotionally. How

00:19:35.559 --> 00:19:44.090
many of you dominate your husband? Be careful.
