00:19:44.090 --> 00:19:52.380
know all of you who dominate. And try to crush
them also, sometimes. I’m requesting you

00:19:52.380 --> 00:19:58.340
now because you are the shakti. You are the
power behind the man. You are the one who

00:19:58.340 --> 00:20:05.429
are going to make them great. You are the
one who are going to build up Sahaja Yoga

00:20:05.429 --> 00:20:12.220
as a potential energy. You are like this Mother
Earth who has to give everything beautiful–all

00:20:12.220 --> 00:20:20.830
these flowers. From where do they come? All
these trees. This Mother Earth looks so simple.

