00:30:01.539 --> 00:30:12.409
this world. Is that the mental projection
has now shown clearly, be with Me, all of

00:30:12.409 --> 00:30:20.820
you. Try to understand. Is a very deep problem,
that if you go to the left or to the right

00:30:20.820 --> 00:30:29.840
you jump into the extremes, into the problems,
and you create problems. So we have to keep

00:30:29.840 --> 00:30:39.269
everybody in the center. And to keeping in
the center, we have to ascend. Now the problem

00:30:39.269 --> 00:30:47.529
is that we have many people who have come
to Sahaja Yoga. This was never achieved before,

00:30:47.529 --> 00:30:55.330
never achieved before. For that, the main
reason was that it was impossible to penetrate

00:30:55.330 --> 00:31:00.549
into the minds of the people, and tell them
what is to be done. Everybody tried their

00:31:00.549 --> 00:31:08.179
level best. Today only I was discussing Buddha.
I said Buddha tried his level best to tell

00:31:08.179 --> 00:31:15.960
people that they should get out of nonsensical
ritualism, and get to their salvation. He

00:31:15.960 --> 00:31:24.499
tried everything. So when He died, they said,
“Alright, he has said not to make any statues;

00:31:24.499 --> 00:31:33.899
we’ll make stupas.” So they made stupas
that they started worshipping. Just the opposite

00:31:33.899 --> 00:31:43.549
what He said, that just now you get your salvation,
your cleansing, introspection and the middle

00:31:43.549 --> 00:31:49.779
path. He even went up to the idea that don’t
have families. With the families means this

00:31:49.779 --> 00:31:57.580
nonsense. You just take to renunciation within
yourself so that you see all these things.

00:31:57.580 --> 00:32:05.070
But as usual, as they were again consolidated
into their nonsensical things, they made big

00:32:05.070 --> 00:32:12.749
stupas and things and worshipped. You see
that in the life of Christ. You see that in

00:32:12.749 --> 00:32:19.669
the life of Mahavira. You see that in the
lives of all the great incarnations and prophets,

00:32:19.669 --> 00:32:30.159
Islam and everything. Same thing has happened,
that they have perverted it. But who has perverted?

00:32:30.159 --> 00:32:43.700
Who has spoiled the whole essence of every
great incarnation? It was spoiled by the disciples

00:32:43.700 --> 00:32:52.379
themselves because they were not realized.
