00:33:13.450 --> 00:33:20.940
think they have become very great. A leader’s
wife thinks she’s the leader herself. If

00:33:20.940 --> 00:33:25.129
you call somebody that “All right, come
and do this job for Me,” the wife thinks

00:33:25.129 --> 00:33:34.159
she has a right on her husband more than Mother
has. Is the women who are the culprit today

00:33:34.159 --> 00:33:39.960
and that’s why I want to warn you. Now I
have seen it. I can point it out, at least

00:33:39.960 --> 00:33:51.370
ten women like that who have done it. And
now the eleventh. It’s just here. This is

00:33:51.370 --> 00:33:56.009
what it is.
