00:34:33.599 --> 00:34:39.730
have gone. They thought that time they have
achieved a lot. This is what I have to tell

00:34:39.730 --> 00:34:46.260
you. If you want to go like that, down in
the history, because this is a very precarious

00:34:46.260 --> 00:34:52.819
time we are facing, and we have to be very,
very careful about ourselves. What are we

00:34:52.819 --> 00:35:00.710
up to? What are we doing? I deal with the
present moment and the present times. And

00:35:00.710 --> 00:35:06.960
I don’t want to say what will happen to
you in future. If you have to go to hell,

00:35:06.960 --> 00:35:11.619
you can go. I’m not going to say who’s
going to go to hell and who’s going to go

00:35:11.619 --> 00:35:17.079
to heavens, but it is for you to decide through
your introspection, to understand what’s

00:35:17.079 --> 00:35:25.240
going to happen. And I have to specially make
a very important request to the women that

00:35:25.240 --> 00:35:29.540
in these modern times, they are the ones who
are going to save the world. Not the men.

00:35:29.540 --> 00:35:35.690
They have done their job before. Now it is
for you to save, with your understanding,

00:35:35.690 --> 00:35:41.839
with your compassion, with your sacrifices,
with your wisdom and the innate love, not

00:35:41.839 --> 00:35:51.200
only your children, your husband, your family,
but the whole world. It is a very good opportunity

00:35:51.200 --> 00:36:02.930
for all of you to do your bit. It has been
a tremendous experience with some of the very

00:36:02.930 --> 00:36:12.800
great Sahaja Yoginis we have. Some of them
have achieved, really, as you can say, the

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:25.630
constant state of bliss. Really. Some of them
have. In the constant state of bliss. Even

00:36:25.630 --> 00:36:32.359
if they are coming, immediately I can feel
they are coming. The whole atmosphere waits

00:36:32.359 --> 00:36:46.349
for them. The whole cosmos, just in complete
respectful attendance, is waiting for their

00:36:46.349 --> 00:36:53.559
arrival. There are women of that quality.
And we have to take them as ideals, and not

00:36:53.559 --> 00:37:01.680
the stupid, useless, vain women. We have to
take them as something great.

00:37:01.680 --> 00:37:07.430
This is what I have to tell you that the potential
within you is very great. Sahaja Yoga should

00:37:07.430 --> 00:37:25.800
not be limited to you or to your children.
