00:39:54.079 --> 00:40:02.500
which is seaworthy, and make a big hole in
it, that boat will be sunk. Even if you have

00:40:02.500 --> 00:40:14.480
the brightest eyes, but a little hole goes
into your eyes, you can’t see the skies.

