00:40:44.690 --> 00:40:50.230
she who’s done so much for me, for Sahaja
Yoga.” And such tremendous respect for the

00:40:50.230 --> 00:40:58.380
women. Even those who have come here, I’ve
seen some of them, have slowly and steadily

00:40:58.380 --> 00:41:06.690
brought their husbands to Sahaja Yoga. Of
course Indians also have some horrid women,

00:41:06.690 --> 00:41:12.119
