00:41:21.740 --> 00:41:28.270
is different, that she has to establish the
dharma in her family. She has to establish

00:41:28.270 --> 00:41:36.430
the beauty of God in her family. She has to
give all that is good to her children, all

00:41:36.430 --> 00:41:41.309
righteousness. She has to be humble. She has
not to raise her voice. If she raises her

00:41:41.309 --> 00:41:46.970
voice, then she spoils her children: she teaches
them how to raise the voice. She has to, in

00:41:46.970 --> 00:41:54.180
a way, obey her husband because children should
obey her. It works; the society is much better

00:41:54.180 --> 00:42:03.280
there than it is here. So this new, also,
a movement of women’s lib and all that,

00:42:03.280 --> 00:42:17.400
is a sign of that
secret work that is going on. Because women
are left-sided, they are sly. They work it

00:42:17.400 --> 00:42:32.599
out very cleverly and cunningly. But you all
could be like Me. You all could achieve all

00:42:32.599 --> 00:42:39.309
My powers much more than men can achieve if
you want to. But you have to get out of your

00:42:39.309 --> 00:42:51.490
small visions and small ideas about glorifying
yourself. I’m sure it will work out if you

00:42:51.490 --> 00:42:58.040
take it upon yourself that we all could do
what Mother is doing today.

