00:43:48.829 --> 00:43:58.099
you have. It’s a grown up child and you
have to look after a grown up child. Be kind

00:43:58.099 --> 00:44:11.319
and attentive. It is very surprising that
you all have not yet learnt those tricks.

00:44:11.319 --> 00:44:48.089
Perhaps your mothers never told you.
