00:45:01.720 --> 00:45:09.390
you can say, a huge big elephant tied with
all kinds of ropes and all kinds of chains

00:45:09.390 --> 00:45:23.430
can go and push forward. In this manner, we
all Sahaja Yogis are going to work it out.

00:45:23.430 --> 00:45:31.260
But the ladies of Sahaja Yoga have to work
it out. They have to see that they give that

00:45:31.260 --> 00:45:38.890
power to their men. If I find any husband
weak, I know it’s the wife who is a nagger

00:45:38.890 --> 00:45:53.290
or who is a dominating person, or who thinks
no end of herself. And if I see a man so powerful,

00:45:53.290 --> 00:46:07.920
I know there’s a woman behind him. It’s
just like electricity and a light and a lamp.

00:46:07.920 --> 00:46:15.410
If the electricity is flowing alright, the
lamp is burning. Absolutely that. But if you

00:46:15.410 --> 00:46:25.900
are identified with these stupid vain women,
then you are lost. You’ll be finished. If

00:46:25.900 --> 00:46:33.549
you know what I am, if you know what I am
saying, and if you try to follow what you

00:46:33.549 --> 00:46:51.910
have to do, then you will immediately see
that Mother is trying to strengthen our roots.

00:46:51.910 --> 00:47:01.359
Because you are the roots of the trees. You
have to give all the nourishment. You have

00:47:01.359 --> 00:47:13.470
to be motherly, sisterly towards all the other
Sahaja Yogis. Not to quarrel, to fight, to

00:47:13.470 --> 00:47:30.670
say hard things. That’s not the job of a
woman. Not to argue but be quiet and watch

00:47:30.670 --> 00:47:37.400
out. Even if they are catching on certain
chakras, you can cleanse them very well as

00:47:37.400 --> 00:47:45.069
wives. You can work it out secretly. You can
do it. Because the problem, though it looks

00:47:45.069 --> 00:47:55.960
so dangerous, and so destructive and shocking,
the keys are in the hands of the women of

00:47:55.960 --> 00:48:06.289
today. They can just solve the problem like
that if they decide and understand their glory

00:48:06.289 --> 00:48:20.799
and their value, and do not make themselves
cheap, hankering after cheap popularity.

00:48:20.799 --> 00:48:38.049
If I have been able to nail down this great
problem to a very precise source of it, and

00:48:38.049 --> 00:48:44.930
if you can manage the source, I’m sure we
can manage Sahaja Yoga. We can manage the

00:48:44.930 --> 00:48:58.800
whole world and the humanity at large is going
to be absolutely saved as that is your desire.
